Name: Apple iPhone 5c 16GB (UNLOCKED) Mobile Phones
Description:
Every feature we add to iPhone must answer yes to one question: Will it make the experience better? So the colors of iPhone 5c received the same intense consideration we apply to everything we make. We even designed the Home screen and wallpaper colors to complement the exterior. As a result, using iPhone is that much more engaging and delightful. -----

With an all-new design, this is iPhone as you’ve never seen it — or held it. iPhone 5c is beautifully, unapologetically plastic, the better to bring its five decidedly uncommon colors to life. Beneath the smooth surface of the seamless outer shell, a steel-reinforced frame provides structural integrity. So iPhone 5c feels reassuringly solid in your hand.

Oh, how quickly things change. Add one of the six Apple?designed cases to your iPhone 5c and it instantly goes from colorfully cool to impossible to ignore. The case design allows the color underneath to show through, creating 30 fun possibilities. So the iPhone 5c Case does more than just protect your phone — it helps it stand out. And it helps you make it yours.Launch your favorite apps. Load your favorite blog.

Long battery life.

The A6 chip is designed to be extremely energy efficient, so you can spend your day taking advantage of all the features and apps on your iPhone. Without worrying about battery life.

iPhone 5c has up to 13 LTE bands. That’s more than any other single model of smartphone. Which means even more iPhone users can experience fast download and upload speeds in more places around the world. Meanwhile, the number of 4G LTE carriers supported by iPhone worldwide continues to grow. So when you’re traveling, you can take advantage of ultrafast 4G LTE networks in more places.

The 8MP iSight camera delivers startlingly sharp photo quality thanks to features like a sophisticated five?element lens. And panorama, which lets you get stunning high?resolution shots of things like packed soccer stadiums. The San Francisco waterfront. Or the high school marching band your friend hired to play “Happy Birthday” outside your window.

New Camera app.

iPhone 5c also comes with a new Camera app that raises your photography game. Now you can shoot images in a square format. And choose from eight live filters than can be applied before or after you take your photo. Use the Instant filter to give a group shot at the beach a vintage color look. Make a sunset even more vivid with the Chrome filter. Or choose Noir to capture a self-portrait in dramatic black and white.

HD video.

Now when you record video in 1080p HD, the new 3x zoom feature lets you get in tighter on your subject. Video image stabilization helps smooth out shaky footage from your high?adrenaline moments. (Running of the Bulls, anyone?) Face detection for up to 10 faces makes sure nobody gets lost in the crowd. And the ability to take still photos while recording video comes in handy when you want to tell that story within a story.

New FaceTime HD camera.

iPhone 5c comes with a new FaceTime HD camera. Larger pixels and an improved backside illumination sensor give it increased sensitivity in low light — great for, say, letting your friend back on the East Coast experience a West Coast sunset with you. You can also make audio?only FaceTime calls with clearer sound than even wideband audio.

Name: Apple iPhone 5c 16GB (UNLOCKED) Mobile Phones
Description:
Every feature we add to iPhone must answer yes to one question: Will it make the experience better? So the colors of iPhone 5c received the same intense consideration we apply to everything we make. We even designed the Home screen and wallpaper colors to complement the exterior. As a result, using iPhone is that much more engaging and delightful. -----

With an all-new design, this is iPhone as you’ve never seen it — or held it. iPhone 5c is beautifully, unapologetically plastic, the better to bring its five decidedly uncommon colors to life. Beneath the smooth surface of the seamless outer shell, a steel-reinforced frame provides structural integrity. So iPhone 5c feels reassuringly solid in your hand.

Oh, how quickly things change. Add one of the six Apple?designed cases to your iPhone 5c and it instantly goes from colorfully cool to impossible to ignore. The case design allows the color underneath to show through, creating 30 fun possibilities. So the iPhone 5c Case does more than just protect your phone — it helps it stand out. And it helps you make it yours.Launch your favorite apps. Load your favorite blog.

Long battery life.

The A6 chip is designed to be extremely energy efficient, so you can spend your day taking advantage of all the features and apps on your iPhone. Without worrying about battery life.

iPhone 5c has up to 13 LTE bands. That’s more than any other single model of smartphone. Which means even more iPhone users can experience fast download and upload speeds in more places around the world. Meanwhile, the number of 4G LTE carriers supported by iPhone worldwide continues to grow. So when you’re traveling, you can take advantage of ultrafast 4G LTE networks in more places.

The 8MP iSight camera delivers startlingly sharp photo quality thanks to features like a sophisticated five?element lens. And panorama, which lets you get stunning high?resolution shots of things like packed soccer stadiums. The San Francisco waterfront. Or the high school marching band your friend hired to play “Happy Birthday” outside your window.

New Camera app.

iPhone 5c also comes with a new Camera app that raises your photography game. Now you can shoot images in a square format. And choose from eight live filters than can be applied before or after you take your photo. Use the Instant filter to give a group shot at the beach a vintage color look. Make a sunset even more vivid with the Chrome filter. Or choose Noir to capture a self-portrait in dramatic black and white.

HD video.

Now when you record video in 1080p HD, the new 3x zoom feature lets you get in tighter on your subject. Video image stabilization helps smooth out shaky footage from your high?adrenaline moments. (Running of the Bulls, anyone?) Face detection for up to 10 faces makes sure nobody gets lost in the crowd. And the ability to take still photos while recording video comes in handy when you want to tell that story within a story.

New FaceTime HD camera.

iPhone 5c comes with a new FaceTime HD camera. Larger pixels and an improved backside illumination sensor give it increased sensitivity in low light — great for, say, letting your friend back on the East Coast experience a West Coast sunset with you. You can also make audio?only FaceTime calls with clearer sound than even wideband audio.

Name: Samsung Galaxy Note 3 N9005 16GB 4G LTE (UNLOCKED) Mobile Phones
Description:
Region Locking: Unlocked

Carrier Locking: Unlocked

Samsung Galaxy Note 3 N9005 4G LTE is the latest addition to Samsung's elite Note series. Introduced on September 04, 2013 at the IFA Berlin, this new phablet flaunts a 5.7-inch Super AMOLED touch display that slightly bigger than its predecessor Galaxy Note 2's 5.5-inch screen. The new handset is visibly thinner so far as width is concerned with 8.3mm thin bezels and smoother edges. The reduction in thickness makes it lighter as well as easier to slide down the pocket. Its multitouch supportive screen offers a Full HD resolution of 1920 x 1080p with 386 pixels packed inside per inch. The bar-form body of the device flaunts a stylish exchangeable textured-back cover. -----

Following in the footsteps of previous Note phablets, the Note 3 also comes with S Pen - only superior. The S Pen now features advanced support for a multitude of new apps and tools including Air Command - a combination of five unique features that provide speed and efficiency to your daily tasks. The 5 features are: 

Action Memo - a handwriting tool that allows you to write notes quickly and even give a command to be executed on the phone. Handwritten notes can also be converted into formatted text hence increasing the speed of input. 

Scrapbook - This feature gathers info from all across the internet as well as the phone storage and displays in the form of a comprehensive card so users can navigate through it easily. 

Screen Write - This unique app takes a mirror image of the page on screen and allows you to write notes on the image so you have a written record of what's important regarding the content on it.

S Finder - It is a powerful feature that allows global search of all content available on the device. You can deploy date/type/size and other filters to locate your data easily. S Finder also finds handwritten content such as Notes as well as Screen Writes.

Pen Window - This app enables you to draw using the S Pen. From sketches to graphical notes, sky is the limit with this creative feature. This unique tool also allows you to literally draw another window on the screen and use it for any task such as opening a browser or running an app. This not only helps in monitoring/performing multiple tasks, but also makes it fun as you go about it.

Specialized apps for the S Pen include enhanced S Note with syncing capability for access from another Samsung device and advanced Easy Clip for quick image cropping by just drawing required borders.

Samsung Galaxy Note 3 N9005 4G LTE boasts a truly powerful 2.3GHz Quad-core processor. A mammoth 3GB of RAM is also included in the chipset which is a first in modern smartphones thus making this device completely lag-free and a super smooth operator. Google's Android OS v4.3 (Jelly Bean) is pre-loaded into the device ROM which provides an internal storage of 16GB and a microSD expansion slot as well. Furthermore, the phablet improves camera specs of the Note 2 thereby introducing a 13MP rear image snapper with HDR, Dual Shot, concurrent movie/image capture and image stabilization features. A 2MP front cam is also available. Both cameras support Full HD 1080p resolution. 

Other key specs of the Samsung Galaxy Note 3 N9005 are- 4G LTE network support (HSPA+ data speed), Wi-Fi, NFC, Bluetooth 4.0, GPS, IR Remote, MHL 2.0, CRI LED Flash and Zero Shutter Lag for cameras, Story Album, S Translator, S Health, S Voice, Samsung Hub, Google & SNS integration, My Magazine for customized personal news from social media and your favorite news feeds, Multi Window toggle for easy multitasking, ChatON app, improved Group Play for both audio/video (which was offered first in Galaxy S4 for up to 5 devices), business ready with Samsung KNOX data security and a 3200mAh battery.

Name: Samsung Galaxy Note 3 N9000 32GB 3G (UNLOCKED) Mobile Phones
Description:
Region Locking: Unlocked

Carrier Locking: Unlocked

Samsung Galaxy Note 3 N9000 is the latest addition to Samsung's elite Note series. Introduced on September 04, 2013 at the IFA Berlin, this new phablet flaunts a 5.7-inch Super AMOLED touch display that slightly bigger than its predecessor Galaxy Note 2's 5.5-inch screen. The new handset is visibly thinner so far as width is concerned with 8.3mm thin bezels and smoother edges. The reduction in thickness makes it lighter as well as easier to slide down the pocket. Its multitouch supportive screen offers a Full HD resolution of 1920 x 1080p with 386 pixels packed inside per inch. The bar-form body of the device flaunts a stylish exchangeable textured-back cover.

Following in the footsteps of previous Note phablets, the Note 3 also comes with S Pen - only superior. The S Pen now features advanced support for a multitude of new apps and tools including Air Command - a combination of five unique features that provide speed and efficiency to your daily tasks. The 5 features are: 

Action Memo - a handwriting tool that allows you to write notes quickly and even give a command to be executed on the phone. Handwritten notes can also be converted into formatted text hence increasing the speed of input. 

Scrapbook - This feature gathers info from all across the internet as well as the phone storage and displays in the form of a comprehensive card so users can navigate through it easily. 

Screen Write - This unique app takes a mirror image of the page on screen and allows you to write notes on the image so you have a written record of what's important regarding the content on it.

S Finder - It is a powerful feature that allows global search of all content available on the device. You can deploy date/type/size and other filters to locate your data easily. S Finder also finds handwritten content such as Notes as well as Screen Writes.

Pen Window - This app enables you to draw using the S Pen. From sketches to graphical notes, sky is the limit with this creative feature. This unique tool also allows you to literally draw another window on the screen and use it for any task such as opening a browser or running an app. This not only helps in monitoring/performing multiple tasks, but also makes it fun as you go about it.

Specialized apps for the S Pen include enhanced S Note with syncing capability for access from another Samsung device and advanced Easy Clip for quick image cropping by just drawing required borders.

Samsung Galaxy Note 3 N9000 boasts a truly powerful 1.9GHz Octa-core (eight cores) processor which is a combination of two Quad-core units of clock-rates 1.9GHz (A15) and 1.3GHz (A7) respectively. A mammoth 3GB of RAM is also included in the chipset which is a first in modern smartphones thus making this device completely lag-free and a super smooth operator. Google's Android OS v4.3 (Jelly Bean) is pre-loaded into the device ROM which provides an internal storage of 32

GB and a microSD expansion slot as well. Furthermore, the phablet improves camera specs of the Note 2 thereby introducing a 13MP rear image snapper with HDR, Dual Shot, concurrent movie/image capture and image stabilization features. A 2MP front cam is also available. Both cameras support Full HD 1080p resolution. 

Other key specs of the Galaxy Note 3 N9000 Octa-core are - 3G network support (HSPA+ data speed), Wi-Fi, NFC, Bluetooth 4.0, GPS, IR Remote, MHL 2.0, CRI LED Flash and Zero Shutter Lag for cameras, Story Album, S Translator, S Health, S Voice, Samsung Hub, Google & SNS integration, My Magazine for customized personal news from social media and your favorite news feeds, Multi Window toggle for easy multitasking, ChatON app, improved Group Play for both audio/video (which was offered first in Galaxy S4 for up to 5 devices), business ready with Samsung KNOX data security and a 3200mAh battery.
